    <title>Women's Advancement contributor: Deepta Chopra</title>
    <description>Dr. Deepta Chopra is a development geographer with a focus on women’s empowerment and the politics of policy processes. Her research interests focusprimarilyon gendered political economy analysis of policies for the empowerment of women and girls, and its core links with unpaid care work.
